---
layout: landing-layout.njk
title: ""
description: "HomeStart — early access. Total cash to close, not just the down payment. Save with a real target, stress-test a payment, walk into the lender prepared. Not a lender. Join the waitlist."
---

{% from "icons-features.njk" import icon %}

<header class="site-header" id="site-header" data-header>
  <div class="header-inner">
    {% include "brand-logo.njk" %}
    <nav aria-label="Primary">
      <ul class="nav-links">
        <li><a href="#showcase">Screens</a></li>
        <li><a href="#features">Inside</a></li>
        <li><a href="#waitlist" class="nav-cta">Join waitlist</a></li>
      </ul>
    </nav>
  </div>
</header>

<main id="main">
  <section class="hero-shell" aria-labelledby="hero-heading">
    <div class="section hero">
      <div class="hero-main">
        <div class="hero-copy">
          <p class="hero-eyebrow">Early access · iOS in development</p>
          <h1 id="hero-heading">Know your real cash to buy a home.</h1>
          <p class="hero-sub">One number for the full cash stack—not just the down payment. See what’s left to save and pressure-test a monthly payment before you apply.</p>
          <div class="hero-actions">
            <a class="btn btn--primary btn--hero" href="#waitlist">Join the waitlist</a>
            <a class="btn btn--secondary" href="#showcase">See preview</a>
          </div>
          <p class="hero-trust">Built for first-time buyers. We don’t lend—we help you get ready.</p>
          <p class="hero-note">We’ll email you at App Store launch—nothing else.</p>
        </div>
        <p class="hero-hook" id="hero-hook">The down payment isn’t the whole number. The total cash is.</p>
        <p class="hero-emotional">Your biggest savings goal deserves a number—not a gut feeling.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--insight section--band-muted" id="why-homestart" aria-labelledby="insight-heading">
    <div class="insight-inner">
      <p class="section-label">The wire is bigger than the down payment</p>
      <h2 id="insight-heading">Closing costs, cash to hold in reserve, movers, first mortgage payment—they land on the same calendar as your down payment.</h2>
      <p class="insight-tight"><strong>{{ site.name }}</strong> rolls them into one total you can save toward, with your balance tracked against it. A future payment sits next to rent and real bills—so the lender isn’t your first reality check.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--preview" id="showcase" aria-labelledby="preview-heading">
    <div class="preview-shell">
      <header class="preview-header">
        <p class="section-label">On your phone, in one scroll</p>
        <h2 id="preview-heading" class="preview-tagline">Target price, full cash to close, what you still need to save, and a monthly payment read—together.</h2>
        <p class="preview-sub">Real iOS UI. Sample numbers. Final polish still landing.</p>
      </header>
      <div class="preview-stage">
        <figure class="app-showcase app-showcase--hero" data-app-preview>
          <div class="mock-frame mock-frame--premium mock-frame--stage">
            <div class="mock-screen mock-screen--photo" role="tabpanel" id="app-preview-panel" aria-labelledby="app-preview-tab-plan">
              <img
                class="app-preview-img"
                src="/images/preview-plan.jpg"
                alt="HomeStart plan overview: target home, closing-cash progress, estimated payment, and savings summary. Sample data."
                width="471"
                height="1024"
                decoding="async"
                fetchpriority="high"
              >
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="preview-tabs" role="tablist" aria-label="Switch app preview screen">
            <button type="button" class="preview-tab" role="tab" id="app-preview-tab-plan" aria-selected="true" aria-controls="app-preview-panel" data-preview-src="/images/preview-plan.jpg" data-preview-alt="HomeStart plan overview: target home, closing-cash progress, estimated payment, and savings summary. Sample data." data-preview-explain="Plan — home price, cash-to-close progress, and estimated payment in one glance.">Plan</button>
            <button type="button" class="preview-tab" role="tab" id="app-preview-tab-numbers" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="app-preview-panel" data-preview-src="/images/preview-numbers.jpg" data-preview-alt="HomeStart numbers view: readiness score and savings, cash-to-close, and payment comfort. Sample data." data-preview-explain="Numbers — how fast you’re saving, how close cash-to-close is, and whether the payment feels survivable.">Numbers</button>
            <button type="button" class="preview-tab" role="tab" id="app-preview-tab-accounts" aria-selected="false" aria-controls="app-preview-panel" data-preview-src="/images/preview-accounts.jpg" data-preview-alt="HomeStart accounts view: linked home fund, progress toward goal, and cash breakdown by purpose. Sample data." data-preview-explain="Accounts — home fund total, distance to goal, and cash split by down payment, closing, and reserves.">Accounts</button>
          </div>
          <p class="showcase__explain" aria-live="polite">Plan — home price, cash-to-close progress, and estimated payment in one glance.</p>
        </figure>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--trust section--band-surface" id="trust" aria-labelledby="trust-heading">
    <p class="section-label" id="trust-heading">No loan desk here</p>
    <ul class="trust-grid" role="list">
      <li class="trust-pill">
        <span class="trust-pill__label">Planning, not lending</span>
        <span class="trust-pill__text">We’re prep work—rate quotes, approvals, and paperwork stay with your lender.</span>
      </li>
      <li class="trust-pill">
        <span class="trust-pill__label">Plaid is optional</span>
        <span class="trust-pill__text">Connect accounts for live balances, or type numbers in by hand.</span>
      </li>
      <li class="trust-pill">
        <span class="trust-pill__label">Your data, your choice</span>
        <span class="trust-pill__text">Connect only what you want. <a href="/security-overview/">See how we protect it →</a></span>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--features section--band-muted" id="features" aria-labelledby="features-heading">
      <header class="section-header">
      <p class="section-label">What you’ll open the app for</p>
      <h2 id="features-heading">Walk in knowing your number</h2>
    </header>
    <div class="features-grid">
      <article class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon-wrap" aria-hidden="true">{{ icon("cash") }}</div>
        <h3>Know the number first</h3>
        <p>Down payment, closing wire, reserves, move-in cash—one target, not four tabs.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon-wrap" aria-hidden="true">{{ icon("savings") }}</div>
        <h3>See the gap shrink</h3>
        <p>Your savings vs. the full stack—updated whenever you add or spend.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon-wrap" aria-hidden="true">{{ icon("afford") }}</div>
        <h3>Stress-test the payment</h3>
        <p>A future mortgage next to rent, income, and what you already owe—before you lock anything in.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon-wrap feature-icon-wrap--accent" aria-hidden="true">{{ icon("link") }}</div>
        <h3>Link—or don’t</h3>
        <p>Plaid for live balances, or enter everything yourself. Same math either way.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="feature-card feature-card--wide">
        <div class="feature-icon-wrap" aria-hidden="true">{{ icon("roadmap") }}</div>
        <h3>Next step, spelled out</h3>
        <p>Ordered milestones and short cues—so you’re not piecing the path together from scattered advice.</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--cta-mid" aria-labelledby="cta-mid-heading">
    <div class="cta-mid">
      <div class="cta-mid__copy">
        <h2 id="cta-mid-heading">App Store is the next beat</h2>
        <p>Waitlist gets the download link the day we ship—no drip campaign, no noise.</p>
      </div>
      <a class="btn btn--primary btn--lg btn--cta-solid" href="#waitlist">Join the waitlist</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--how section--band-surface" id="how-it-works" aria-labelledby="how-heading">
    <header class="section-header">
      <p class="section-label" id="how-heading">How it comes together</p>
      <h2 class="visually-hidden">How HomeStart works</h2>
    </header>
    <div class="steps">
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num">01</div>
        <h3>Start with your numbers</h3>
        <p>Income, rent, debts, and savings on hand.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num">02</div>
        <h3>Name a real target</h3>
        <p>Pick a price band or monthly max, then fold in taxes, insurance, timing, and the full cash to close.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num">03</div>
        <h3>Close the gap</h3>
        <p>Refresh savings when life shifts. Link with Plaid—or skip it. The roadmap stays in front of you.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--audience section--band-muted" id="audience" aria-labelledby="audience-heading">
    <div class="audience-inner">
      <p class="section-label" id="audience-heading">Your first set of keys—not a side hustle</p>
      <p class="audience-lead">Not portfolio buyers. Not flippers. Not another spreadsheet you’ll abandon.</p>
      <p class="audience-outro">One lane toward the front door you’re actually going to unlock.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--waitlist" id="waitlist" aria-labelledby="waitlist-heading">
    <div class="waitlist waitlist--premium">
      <p class="waitlist__badge">First in line for the App Store link</p>
      <h2 id="waitlist-heading">Reserve your spot</h2>
      <p class="waitlist__lead">We email you when the app goes live. That’s the whole pitch.</p>
      <ul class="waitlist__bullets" role="list">
        <li>Download link on launch day</li>
        <li>Rare, short updates if we slip a milestone</li>
        <li>One-click unsubscribe</li>
      </ul>
      <form class="waitlist-form waitlist-form--premium" id="waitlist-form" novalidate>
        <div class="field-wrap">
          <label class="visually-hidden" for="waitlist-email">Email address</label>
          <input type="email" id="waitlist-email" name="email" autocomplete="email" placeholder="you@email.com" required inputmode="email">
        </div>
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn--primary btn--submit btn--lg btn--cta-solid" id="waitlist-submit">Join the waitlist</button>
      </form>
      <p class="waitlist__fineprint">Waitlist and launch only. <a href="/privacy-policy/">Privacy Policy</a></p>
      <div class="waitlist-status" id="waitlist-status" role="status" aria-live="polite"></div>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>

<footer class="site-footer">
  <div class="footer-inner">
    <span class="footer-brand">{{ site.name }}</span>
    <ul class="footer-links">
      <li><a href="/privacy-policy/">Privacy</a></li>
      <li><a href="/terms-of-service/">Terms</a></li>
      <li><a href="/security-overview/">Security</a></li>
      <li><a href="mailto:{{ site.supportEmail }}">Contact</a></li>
    </ul>
    <p class="footer-meta">© {{ site.copyrightYear }} {{ site.companyLegalName }}</p>
  </div>
</footer>

<script>
  (function () {
    var h = document.getElementById("site-header");
    if (!h) return;
    function tick() {
      h.classList.toggle("is-scrolled", window.scrollY > 8);
    }
    tick();
    window.addEventListener("scroll", tick, { passive: true });
  })();
</script>
